1948;;Larceny;;American;;George Sherman;;John Payne, Joan Caulfield, Dan Duryea, Shelley Winters;;film noir;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Larceny_(1948_film);;Con man Rick Maxon (Payne) tries to swindle war widow Deborah (Caulfied) into giving up her savings for a nonexistent memorial. When Rick falls in love with Deborah he has pangs of remorse. But he reckons without enamored moll Tory (Winters) and his gang boss Randall (Duryea).